4. now open client.java and search for:
[code=java]
if(playerEquipment[playerWeapon] == 5698 && specialAmount > 24){
        specdelay = 2;
        specialAtk(true, 25, 252, 0x426);
        getHit(8);
        usingSpecial = true;
}
[/code]
5. add above it this:
[code=java]
if(playerEquipment[playerWeapon] == WEAPONID && specialAmout > 49 {
        specialAmout -= 50
        stillgfx(gfxid, absX, absY);
        hitDiff = misc.random(playerMaxHit+playerMaxHit/2);
